title: Koisuru nante Kiitenai
original_name: 恋するなんて聞いてない
sinopse:
Matsumoto Kanna is an office lady at a critical point(?) in her life, but for some reason she ends up being taught work by her contemporary, the boring, plain-faced Noda Haruki.

(Source: MU)

Included one-shots:
Tadaima, Okaeri.
Haru nanka Konai
